casebody.data:
CINTAS CORPORATION, petitioner,
v.
EQUAL EMPLOYMENT OPPORTUNITY COMMISSION. No. 12-1347. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013. Case below, 699 F.3d 884 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied. Justice BREYER took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
